{"tid":1270764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【全民抗爭】仲考慮緊今日出唔出嚟嘅市民入嚟","createTime":"2019-07-01T02:43:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T08:48:25.000Z","uid":51814,"like":133,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6eed076e2e40ad5cb4cee635c4809935f209b869","tid":1270764,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:43:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我唔理你係黃係藍係人係鬼，你手持香港永久居民身份證，就有義務保護香港人嘅身份，你睇下撑警嗰幾萬隻冒牌腥港人已經影衰哂我地型像柒出國際，我地要出嚟澄清香港嘅示威者係有文化修養嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">如果有小朋友嘅帶埋出嚟！<br />\n<br />\n如果有老人家陪佢出嚟！<br />\n<br />\n如果有廢老引佢出嚟！<br />\n<br />\n如果有工人請佢出嚟！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好諗人地出夠人啦我唔駛出！<br />\n<br />\n唔好信林鄭會改變聽香港民意！<br />\n<br />\n唔好驚警察會清場，記得6.16！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">見證全香港人一齊對抗極權嘅一天，話俾狗官知我地先係代表香港</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">早啲出嚟，塞爆金鐘！</span></span>"},{"pid":"0dfbfd974fd3d3b5ca5dd5f6515f5de93441ec2e","tid":1270764,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:48:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d7452d3c244e9558ae5bec77e40ee9e8f40ddf66","tid":1270764,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:54:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eac5032260ae20395a66db16806f9f9e9b3a43e2","tid":1270764,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:01:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f8837dc84dc821c979c0921a8c9c2c5d8bf876c2","tid":1270764,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:07:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8e9082e94b097eec1b704631c770e0f7d773b3d7","tid":1270764,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:09:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d1b6e9ae7dccc8075dd27a192ebd2f415c6e8dea","tid":1270764,"uid":263618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:09:35.000Z","msg":"push